onological studies, bringing to light writings hitherto hidden in the archives.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Apr 2022) 0aChronology, HistoricalvEarly works to 1800. 0aChronology, HistoricalyEarly works to 1800. 0aChronology. 0aHistory, AncientvChronology. 0aHistory, AncientxChronology. 4aEarly Modern Studies. 4aEuropean history. 4aHistory of ideas. 4aHistory, Art History, and Archaeology. 4aLiterary Theory, Criticism, and History. 4aLiterary studies: c 1600 to c 1800. 4aReligion and Theology. 4aScience and Technology. 4ac 1500 onwards to present day. 7aHISTORY / Modern / 17th Century.2bisacsh  aIsaac Newton, Chronology, Prophecy, Early Modern Scholarship.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertAmsterdam University Press Complete eBook-Package 2021z978311074322708iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus PP Package 2021 Part 2z978311074335708iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2021 Englishz978311075400108iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE History 2021 Englishz978311075408708iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE History 2021z9783110753851oZDB-23-DEG40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978904855428740uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9789048554287423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9789048554287/original  a978-3-11-074322-7  Amsterdam University Press Complete eBook-Package 2021b2021  a978-3-11-074335-7  DG Plus PP Package 2021 Part 2b2021  a978-3-11-075400-1  EBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2021 Englishb2021  a978-3-11-075408-7  EBOOK PACKAGE History 2021 Englishb2021  aEBA_CL_HICS  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_HICS  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA17SSHEE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DE